Health Fitness App

Simple ncurses-based UI for Health Fitness Application

How to compile:

For Ubuntu-based Distros:
gcc -I/usr/include/postgresql/ main.c -lpq -lmenu -lform -lncurses

The location of the postgresql library might be different depending on 
your Linux distro.

How to run:
./a.out

Video of usage: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eVlA17kvlRo

If you are a TA, I've uploaded the rest of the project to the carleton brightspace submission. 
